The Philosophy Book: Big Ideas Simply Explained
by Will Buckingham, Douglas Burnham, Peter J. King and Clive Hill
DK Publishing | October 2010 | ISBN: 0756668611 | PDF | 352 pages | 24.3 mb &lt;a href=&quot;
